WEBVTT

00:02:29.444 --> 00:02:30.601
Ningependa kusema,

00:02:30.625 --> 00:02:34.069
Serikali pekee ndiyo inaweza kujenga
mazingira muhimu

00:02:34.093 --> 00:02:35.744
kwa ajili ya ustawi wa uchumi.

00:02:36.549 --> 00:02:41.387
Uchumi hustawi pale biashara zinaweza kuanzishwa kwa urahisi.

00:02:41.411 --> 00:02:44.783
wamiliki wa biashara hujiekea vyanzo vipya vya mapato,

00:02:44.807 --> 00:02:47.258
ajira zinazoongezwa katika uchumi

00:02:47.282 --> 00:02:50.846
na mapato ya kodi ili kufadhili miradi ya umma.

00:02:51.504 --> 00:02:53.967
Biashara mpya zinamnufaisha kila mtu.

00:02:54.415 --> 00:02:57.245
Na ni kipimo muhimu cha ukuaji wa uchumi,

00:02:57.269 --> 00:03:01.220
Benki ya Dunia ina kipimo kinachotwa
"Mazingira ya Kufanya Biashara,"